•Active participation in handling the deployment and development activities of the first production release of the

PROJECTS
Seamless Data Migration to Redshift Data Lake from Multiple Sources
•Crafted a cloud-specific data migration solution utilizing AWS DMS and customized ETL tools. Devised au-
tomation scripts with Python and the boto3 module to efficiently migrate data from multiple sources to the
AWS Redshift data lake while implementing rigorous data quality checks.
•Implemented job orchestration with MWAA Airflow and integrated AWS SNS to establish an alert mechanism
for streamlined end-to-end job management.
AWS QuickSight Object Migration.
•Developed a highly efficient automated solution from the ground up, utilizing Python and the AWS APIs with
the boto3 module to automate the migration of QuickSight Objects between same and cross-accounts.
•By streamlining the migration of QuickSight objects to diverse environments for agile methodologies and multiple
use cases across various accounts, this module facilitated automated migration.
Meta-data Comparison Project.
•Created an efficient Python script, which employs intricate SQL queries to scrutinize two schemas across different
databases for discrepancies, and generates a comprehensive summary in a CSV file, facilitating further analysis.
•By incorporating this development process, basic checks like identifying row-level discrepancies became a breeze.
Additionally, performance was drastically enhanced by 90x for data that had been migrated to AWS Redshift
through diverse sources like Postgres and MicroDBs.

Hello, I’m Kish, and I'm thrilled to have the opportunity to introduce myself to you. Life, for me, is a journey of discovery, growth, and the relentless pursuit of excellence. In these pages, I aim to provide you with a glimpse into my world, sharing not just my accomplishments but also the values and experiences that have shaped me into the person I am today.
**Background**
Born and raised in India, my upbringing was marked by a blend of diverse cultures, values, and traditions. Growing up in such an environment instilled in me a deep appreciation for diversity, empathy, and the importance of understanding different perspectives. It laid the foundation for my curiosity about the world and a desire to explore beyond the confines of familiarity.
**Education**
I embarked on my educational journey with a thirst for knowledge and a passion for learning. Graduating from NIT surat with distinction, I pursued my interests in Computer Engineering with unwavering dedication. During my academic pursuits, I not only acquired theoretical knowledge but also honed practical skills through hands-on projects, internships, and extracurricular activities.
**Professional Experience**
My professional journey has been an exhilarating ride filled with challenges, triumphs, and invaluable lessons. From my early days as a Data engineer at Infosys, I've had the privilege of working with talented individuals and visionary leaders who have inspired and mentored me along the way. Each role, whether it was in Data Engineering, taught me something new and contributed to my growth as a professional.
**Passions and Hobbies**
Beyond the confines of work and academia, I find solace and inspiration in pursuing my passions and hobbies. Whether it's immersing myself in the world of literature, exploring the great outdoors, or experimenting with culinary delights in the kitchen, I believe in the importance of maintaining a healthy work-life balance. These pursuits not only rejuvenate my spirit but also fuel my creativity and zest for life.
**Aspirations**
Looking ahead, my aspirations are fueled by a desire to make a positive impact on the world around me. Whether it's through my professional endeavors, philanthropic initiatives, or personal relationships, I strive to leave a lasting legacy of kindness, compassion, and excellence. With every challenge I face and every opportunity I seize, I am committed to pushing the boundaries of what is possible and inspiring others to do the same.
**Conclusion**
In conclusion, I am deeply grateful for the experiences, opportunities, and relationships that have shaped my journey thus far. As I continue to navigate the twists and turns of life's path, I do so with an open heart, a curious mind, and an unwavering belief in the power of dreams. Thank you for taking the time to get to know me, and I look forward to the adventures that lie ahead.
